item.title: Features
item.dc:creator: pfadmin
item.content:encoded: [vc_row css=".vc_custom_1423485814431{padding-top: 50px !important;padding-bottom: 50px !important;background-color: #ffffff !important;}" widthopt="" fixedbg="" footerrow=""][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="1238" border_color="grey" img_link_large="" img_link_target="_self" img_size="large"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_custom_heading text="Quick Setup" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:16|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:4px" google_fonts="font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:500%20bold%20regular%3A500%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]You can perform the setup of your theme in minutes. Moreover, you can choose any of our demo websites and create it exactly the same.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="5px"][vc_custom_heading text="Front End Upload System" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:16|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:4px" google_fonts="font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:500%20bold%20regular%3A500%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]You can make sure your visitors upload to your website with this system. You can allow them to upload either for free or you can determine a price per item. You can make additional pricing in special listings with Featured Points feature.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="5px"][vc_custom_heading text="Paypal Recurring and Direct Payments" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:16|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:4px" google_fonts="font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:500%20bold%20regular%3A500%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]Thanks to Point Finders system which is fully integrated with Paypal, you can allow your visitors to choose Paypal Recurring or Paypal Direct Payment options when uploading their items. In addition to that, you can also run your system with bank transfer option and offline payment mode.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="5px"][vc_custom_heading text="Paypal IPN System" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:16|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:4px" google_fonts="font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:500%20bold%20regular%3A500%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]You can leave the tracking of processes such as cancellation and stopping of agreement in Recurring Payments to Point Finder IPN system. In such cases, it will make instantaneous changes in the system, saving you a lot of work.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="5px"][vc_custom_heading text="Order Tracking System" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:16|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:4px" google_fonts="font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:500%20bold%20regular%3A500%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]Point Finder tracks every payment that is due and presents you a detailed report. You can track payments and processes for any items your users have uploaded to your system.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=".vc_custom_1422536038507{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 40px !important;background-color: #ffffff !important;}" widthopt="" fixedbg="" footerrow=""][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_custom_heading text="Customizable Info Windows" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:16|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:4px" google_fonts="font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:500%20bold%20regular%3A500%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]You can customize information windows which open when you click on points with this feature. You can adjust their color, size and content as you like from the admin panel.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="5px"][vc_custom_heading text="Customizable Points" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:16|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:4px" google_fonts="font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:500%20bold%20regular%3A500%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]You can create your points easily without making any uploads, either for categories or for each item, thanks to Custom Point Config feature that we offer to you.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="5px"][vc_custom_heading text="Multiple Point at Same Place" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:16|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:4px" google_fonts="font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:500%20bold%20regular%3A500%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]You can easily add with this system which has been made for multiple items located at the same address and show your visitors all of them.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="5px"][vc_custom_heading text="Geolocation feature" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:16|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:4px" google_fonts="font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:500%20bold%20regular%3A500%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]We used Google Map Geolocation feature in Point Finder to the best of our ability. You can position your visitors, and easily show your properties or items in specified distance.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="5px"][vc_custom_heading text="Map Styling" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:16|text_align:left|color:%23333333|line_height:4px" google_fonts="font_family:Roboto%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C500%2C500italic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:500%20bold%20regular%3A500%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]You can create personalized maps on Point Finder Google Map by styling.
